Class CompositeResultSetManager

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
QueryResultSet
public class CompositeResultSetManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements QueryResultSet

The CompositeResultSetManager is used in order to query the local instance of NCIA as well as any other grid instances. It gathers together the results from all nodes and sends them back to the UI.
